How to Manage Chaos:
	- John

Dealing with things going wrong.

First time problems:
	- naked ruby team photo shoots mid-event
	- breakfast arrived previous sunday...

5 Steps to deal with chaos
	Assessment - focus on major things
		- food, venue, medical emergency, etc.
	Prevention - have access to your materials al lthe time
		- use gitbooks for monitoring materials
		- SLEEP everyone should sleep
		- Bus factor. not all responsibilities through one person
		- clear points of contat for specific issue/topics
			+ give backups
		- schedule in half hour blocks.
	Preparation - hackcon
	Response
	Recover
